title: Ebro In The Morning - The Queen Of England + Donda 2 + White ISH
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 2/23/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are in the studio talking about the Donda 2 Liver Stream, the alleged death of the Queen of England from Hollywood Unlocked, and much more. Will the crew play White-ISH Wednesday?

Get excited for the gurus to help solve your problems and the latest news with Flashing Lights. All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
